            "Implement Kafka producer for events",
            "Configure configurable event rates (10-50 events/sec)"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Infrastructure as Code (Terraform)",
          "days": "Week 3, Days 4-7",
          "tasks": [
            "Initialize Terraform project",
