            "Impl Query 3: Top 10 Products (Dense Rank)",
            "Impl Query 4: Trader Fulfillment Rate (Lag/Lead)",
            "Impl Query 5: Monthly Sales Trends (Moving Avg)",
            "Impl Query 6: Customer Segmentation RFM (Ntile)",
            "Impl Query 7: Stock Turnover (Percent Rank)",
            "Impl Query 8: Price Fluctuations (Percentile)",
            "Impl Query 9: Peak Order Hours (Row Number)",
            "Impl Query 10: Revenue Forecasting (Regression/Trend)",
            "Run ETL jobs: Raw -> Transform -> Curated (Parquet)"
          ]
        }
